971
01:12:01,663 --> 01:12:02,997
Not everything.

972
01:12:05,124 --> 01:12:08,836
Your father was, a very special man.

973
01:12:09,963 --> 01:12:14,050
He provided extra services.

974
01:12:16,511 --> 01:12:18,471
Oh, my God.

975
01:12:18,596 --> 01:12:21,724
Your dad didn't say,
''Stick with Miss Crock. You'll get ahead.''

976
01:12:21,808 --> 01:12:25,395
He said, ''Stick with Miss Crock
and you'll get head.''

977
01:12:25,478 --> 01:12:29,023
Would you butt out? We're talking here!

978
01:12:29,107 --> 01:12:30,692
Yuck!

979
01:12:31,943 --> 01:12:34,487
Let's move!

980
01:12:38,783 --> 01:12:41,035
-Can you see them?
-They're on the third floor.

981
01:12:41,869 --> 01:12:42,870
Oh, man!

982
01:12:42,954 --> 01:12:45,081
That's why l couldn't compare to my dad?

983
01:12:45,164 --> 01:12:48,459
Now, don't be silly. lt's just that...

984
01:12:48,543 --> 01:12:51,838
...your father was very gifted.

985
01:12:51,921 --> 01:12:55,008
-That's some big shoes to fill.
-l don't wanna hear this!

986
01:12:55,091 --> 01:12:58,177
Man, you must've been a total let down.

987
01:12:58,261 --> 01:13:00,847
No wonder she ransomed you
with an empty suitcase.

988
01:13:00,930 --> 01:13:03,349
That suitcase wasn't empty.

989
01:13:04,851 --> 01:13:06,227
